node.text:
The 30th of October, Café 124 will move away from its present location in Via Sottocorno. Bad news, we know. The good news is, next time you'll come to us you'll be allowed to drink our extractions, from espresso to V60 to Aeropress... even after 3.30pm! 
Il 30 di ottobre Café 124 lascerà la sede di via Sottocorno. Inaspettatamente, ci spiace. Ma la buona notizia è che presto sarete in grado di venire da noi a qualsiasi ora della giornata e godervi l'espresso della settimana anche dopo le 15.30!

We are looking for a new place and we’ll find it soon. But if you know of any commercial activity, eg a bookshop, where the coffees from Café 124 would be a good match, write to us!! #cafe124 ☕️♥️
Who doesn’t love a good pain au chocolat with flat white as a late breakfast? Make sure you swing by this week to try this delicious combo! ☕️♥️ #cafe124
Here’s an idea for your next breakfast: this Colombia batch brew’s acidity matches perfectly with the sweetness of pistachio croissant! What are you waiting? 🤤☕️ #cafe124

Aaaaa latte art, never enough isn’t it? 😻 Especially on a flat white, especially when explained by @danieledonateo! What’s you fav latte art? 
P.S. Today is the last day of @hostmilano are you going to be there? ☕️♥️ #cafe124
Cupping alert 🚨 Tomorrow 11am we will have the opportunity to taste Colombia & Costa Rica from @coffee_hat and a special Honduras called Geisha by @timwendelboe! #cafe124

How should do you steam milk? Before a beautiful latte art the key is to steam it properly: it doesn’t look easy and it definitely isn’t. Make sure not to reheat the same milk, to keep it cool in the fridge and to always clean the wand, then go & make some tasty coffee! 🥛😻 #cafe124

& this is what happened during Coffee for Dummies workshop on Saturday! We listened to @nastialavista that introduced us to third wave coffee world, tasted @niceandnastybar coffees prepared with different techniques and at the end learned how to make v60 and aeropress! It was amazing, we were many & also a special friend participated 🐶! See you next time! #cafe124 #coffeefordummies

What is exactly a flat white? If you want a strong espresso taste but you can’t renounce to the creamy silky foam, flat white is for you. Served in 180ml glass with a delicious and thinner foam, is more concentrated than cappuccino & latte and you’ll be able to feel more the coffee taste rather than milk. Some say that cures everything ☕️♥️ #cafe124

Workshop alert 🚨 COFFEE FOR DUMMIES by @niceandnastybar! Un’occasione perfetta per rispondere a tutte le domande che ci avete fatto e approfondire con una breve lezione teorica e una parte pratica il mondo dello specialty coffee o terza onda! Noi non stiamo nella pelle... e voi? See you at 11am ☕️♥️ #cafe124 #coffeefordummies

Let’s get a bit nerdy, here’s our @danieledonateo dealing with TDS. For newly coffee lovers let us explain, basically it helps us measure the level of extraction of coffee that is around 18-23% for a well-balanced cup of coffee, with a good level of complexity and sweetness. ☕️♥️ #cafe124milan

Cupping alert 🚨 We used this beautiful latte art to catch your attention & we hope you have no programs for tomorrow because if you’ve never been to one of our cuppings you can’t miss this one! See you in Via Sottocorno, 17 at 11am tomorrow!

Old but gold sandwich but new cups on the background! No ideas for your lunch break? Here’s one... ps don’t forget to pair it with a specialty coffee that our staff will suggest you! 😋☕️🥪 #cafe124milan
Celebrating International Coffee Day 🎉with our new custom cup! We wanted to ask something: what does coffee mean for you? Let us know! #cafe124milan
We bet you know how timing is important in specialty coffee, this is why you should always rely on your barista to unlock all the coffee power! ☕️♥️ #cafe124milan
This morning’s cupping was amazing, artistic, tasty & funny as well. Here’s a little recap of what happened, we hope to see you at the next one!! #cafe124milan

Cupping alert 🚨 Domani cupping artistico a tutto tondo: i meravigliosi edifici abbandonati della serie 'Solo la Luce' fotografati da @diegomorra, che espone opere di grande e piccolo formato, colonna sonora prodotta dall'handpan di Biagio Vallefuoco e tre caffè da non perdere: Bolivia e El Salvador di @thebarnberlin, Kenya di @coffee_hat! ☕️♥️ #cafe124milan
Your daily dealer of filter coffee aka pure happiness! We’re always waiting for you ♥️☕️ #cafe124milan
Helloooo everyone! First things first, it’s Monday and we want to introduce you our new entry, custom cups, they’re lovely aren’t they? 😻☕️ #cafe124milan
Would you ever be able to define what coffee is? For us, coffee is inexplicable, like the sky (have a look to the quote on the calendar of today)!♥️☕️#cafe124milan
No plans for tomorrow? As every Saturday, at 11:00 we organize a cupping session and this time we’ll taste... shhh it’s a secret! Drop by to solve the mystery 😉
A proper jewel you can have running around for #MilanoFashionWeek is this new entry: ricotta, blueberries & raspberries! 🥐♥️ special thanks to @marchese.onwheels #mfw2019 #cafe124milan
But honestly what’s better than steamed milk or flat white? Best way to start your day with us! ☕️♥️ #cafe124milan
We love to make coffee for people who enjoy drinking it 🖤☕️ #cafe124milan
Loved our handpan + cupping combo? Next Saturday we will do it again! Are you in? #cafe124milan
Life is unpredictable but about our Saturday’s cupping you can be sure ☕️ #cafe124milan
